_json.gridTitle: The Great Big Giant Marek's Disease FAQ
_json.description: Are there any medications I can give specifically for Marek's? No cures. -St. Johns Wort, specifically Hypericum, Turmeric + Black Pepper, specifically Curcumin with Bioperene (thought to be a blood cleanser), Vitamin B ("Super B") Complex, Nutritional Yeast (check label to be sure of high vitamin B-12/Thiamin percentages!), Cold-pressed Coconut oil (help vitamin absorption in general), Cranberry, specifically high quality whole berry (can be chopped, mashed, or cooked into a sauce)
